<h2>ğŸ§± List Operations Master Guide</h2>

<h3>Step 1: Creating and Basic Operations</h3>
<div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 10px 0;">
    <pre style="background: #263238; color: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; overflow-x: auto;">
// ============ LIST CREATION & SETUP ============
when green flag clicked

// CREATE A NEW LIST (do this once!)
// Click "Make a List" in Variables section
// Name it: shopping-list
// Choose: For all sprites (shared) or this sprite only

// INITIALIZE THE LIST (clear old items)
delete (all v) of [shopping-list v]

